 Customer FAQ Template

## 1. How do I reset my password?
Answer: Go to the login page, click "Forgot password," and follow the instructions. You’ll receive a reset link via email.

## 2. How do I upgrade my plan?
Answer: Navigate to your account settings → Billing → Upgrade Plan. Select your desired plan and confirm payment.

## 3. How can I contact support?
Answer: You can reach out via our live chat or email support@example.com. Our team responds within 24 hours.

## 4. How do I download my purchased content?
Answer: Go to “My Downloads” → Click the download button next to the item. Ensure your browser allows downloads.

## 5. What if I have a refund request?
Answer: Refunds are processed according to our refund policy. Submit a request via support@example.com.
